headline: GTA Online
subtitle: THE CRIMINAL ENTERPRISES
content:
The Southern San Andreas economy is in crisis. Gas prices have spiked to their highest levels in decades, retail supply chains are in turmoil, and to top it off a ferocious heatwave is gripping the state....

But this is Los Santos, where every dark fiscal cloud has a silver lining. On the black market, business is booming, with stacks of opportunities to make bank. Just remember: opportunities can come from unexpected places, so keep your phone close. A classified contact will be in touch...
